title: DNSK in the Mix (Live DJ Set 2016-08-10)
description:
DNSK in the Mix (Live DJ Set 2016-08-10)


Broadcasted at dnsk.dj 2016-08-10

DNSK in the Mix is a webradio concept that I am developing.

My site dnsk.dj will serve my stream when I mix live and I will announce on Twitter andwhen I do.

This DJ set consists of techno and tech house.
